channel.title: Anyone who wants to join me
channel.description: I know this might not be in the right section :). I would like to send an invation to all the good coders out there. You all are probably dying to hear what I have to say so. If your a good coder do you want to create a beast skill with me? I will allow 3 coders along the journey with me. ( 4 people in all ) I will not say what the skill is unless you join the team so people don't leech. If you would like to join us do it in this format: *age *experience with skills *msn ( if this gets locked please move it to where its suppost to be or tell me where it should go ). Thanks, No1toldme2
